These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, pall-mall, cain, oliveros
City: miami, marseilles, hamburg, berlin
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, australian, russian, polish
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the mexican is not to the left of the mexican##8
 3. the polish is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the mexican is not to the right of the mexican##8
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
 8. the person traveling to berlin is between the australian and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the polish is the person traveling to hamburg##1
10. the polish is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
11. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
12. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the pall-mall-smoker##5
13. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the left of the polish##8
14. the pall-mall-smoker is the russian##1
15. the pall-mall-smoker is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Cigar         | chaman     | pall-mall   | oliveros | cain |
| City   | marseilles | berlin   | miami   | hamburg  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| Nationality     | mexican    | russian | australian     | polish    |

