.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
4 different games are played: snooker, domino, chess, whist
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dressmaker, nurse, fisherman
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, documentary, comedy, scientific
 1. the nurse is between the person watching western movies and the dressmaker##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person watching scientific movies##8
 5. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the dressmaker##8
 6. the person playing whist is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
 8. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
 9. the bartender is the person watching documentary movies##1
10. the nurse is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
11. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the nurse##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
14. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the nurse##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the dressmaker##8
18. the person playing domino is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Game          | whist     | domino | snooker | chess  |
| Job   | dressmaker    | nurse  | fisherman | bartender |
| Movie-Genre           | comedy | scientific | western    | documentary  |

