.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, march, november
City: nizza, new-york, san-francisco, berlin
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, chestnut, pink, fuchsia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person who likes mauve##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person traveling to nizza##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
 7. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 9. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to nizza is not to the left of the person who likes chestnut##8
12. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | february    | november   | march | august |
| City   | nizza     | san-francisco  | berlin   | new-york      |
