 4. the craftsman house is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsrose##2
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
 6. the fan of pop is not to the right of the craftsman house##8
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
10. the person who growsrose is the fan of pop##1
11. the fan of d&b is not to the right of the victorian house##8
12. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
