 4. the fan of indie is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 6. the fan of techno is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 7. the fan of classical is not to the left of the analyst##8
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the left of the architect##8
10. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
11. the fan of electronic is between the architect and the person watching drama movies##2
12. the chef is on the right of the fan of techno##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
14. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
