 2. the person who likes emerald is not to the left of the person playing canasta##8
 3. the person who likes emerald is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 5. the person who likes grey is the person eating artichoke##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person eating blueberry##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the person eating zucchini##6
 8. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
10. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
11. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing chess##1
12. the person playing monopoly is not the person eating tomato##6
13. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the person who likes emerald is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
