 9. the colonial house is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the art-deco house##7
10. the colonial house is not to the left of the pakistani##8
11. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
12. the engineer is not to the right of the farmhouse house##8
13. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
14. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
