.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, aristoff, vegafina, oliveros
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
4 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, hamster, cat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, drama, superhero, action
 1. the vegafina-smoker is the owner of the cat##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 3. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 4. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
 8. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
 9. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
10. the aristoff-smoker is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
12. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5

